msgstr "ເປີເຊັນສ່ວນຫຼຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນເມື່ອຄລິກໃສ່ປຸ່ມສ່ວນຫຼຸດ"

#. module: pos_discount
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/pos_discount/static/src/app/services/pos_store.js:0
msgid ""
"The discount product seems misconfigured. Make sure it is flagged as 'Can be"
" Sold' and 'Available in Point of Sale'."
msgstr ""
"ສິນຄ້າສ່ວນຫຼຸດເບິ່ງຄືວ່າຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າໄດ້ໝາຍເອົາ 'ສາມາດຂາຍໄດ້' ແລະ 'ມີໃ"
"ຫ້ໃຊ້ໃນຈຸດຂາຍ'."

#. module: pos_discount
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:pos_discount.field_pos_config__discount_product_id
msgid "The product used to apply the discount on the ticket."
msgstr "ສິນຄ້າທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອນຳໃຊ້ສ່ວນຫຼຸດໃນໃບບິນ."

#. module: pos_discount
